column8: He put you up to this? Look, hon, why don't you get on with your business, then. But you can't leave empty-handed, that's the rule, so take your pick, my treat! Nothing for him, though.
You know, you're much more generous than you get credit for, Your Majesty! I'm feeling pretty generous, myself, so here! I want you to have this.
Yeah, what do you want? Oh!
What can I do for you, hon?
Hey, Your Royal Majesty, to what do I owe the pleasure?
As you wish, Your Royal Majesty.
